<h6 style="text-align: center;">MANGAL CHAND JAIN</h6>
<p style="font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;">Mangal Chand brings with him a more than two decades of experience in developing close to 1200 acres of land near Bangalore, Hyderabad, Kodaikanal and Jaipur. His recent project - Sukh Shanti-the retirement home has been running successfully for the past two years.</p>
<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="30px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="1" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation="fadeInDown" width="1/3" icons_position="left"][vc_empty_space height="50px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="1" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_single_image image="1124" img_size="full" add_caption="yes" alignment="center"][vc_empty_space height="30px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="1" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_column_text]</p>
<h6 style="text-align: center;">ANANTHARAM V VARAYUR</h6>
<p style="font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;">AnantharamVarayur has spent close to three decades in the IT sector and has an unbridled passion to develop active senior living. He is the Executive Director at BNI Bangalore and has helped more than 2000 members develop their business successfully. Ananthram along with Sumathy have travelled to over 15 countries to understand the culture of that place and retirement homes.</p>
<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="30px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="1" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation="fadeInRight" width="1/3" icons_position="left"][vc_empty_space height="50px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="1" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_single_image image="1125" img_size="full" add_caption="yes" alignment="center"][vc_empty_space height="30px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="1" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_column_text]</p>
<h6 style="text-align: center;">SUMATHY ANANTHARAM</h6>
<p style="font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;">Sumathy Anantharam nurses a passion to serve the senior community. She has close to three decades of experience in the IT sector. She completed the ISB Women Entrepreneurship Program and mentors young entrepreneur helping them choose the right path in their business career.</p>
<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="30px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="1" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" hide_bg_image_on_tablet="" hide_bg_image_on_mobile=""][vc_column icons_position="left"][vc_empty_space height="46px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][trx_sc_title title_style="default" title_tag="h3" title_align="center" link_style="default" title="Our Partners"][vc_empty_space height="36px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="1" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_tta_tabs alignment="center" active_section="1"][vc_tta_section title="Dr. Shyam Sunder" tab_id="1553234971201-bcfdd58b-8fbc"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner icons_position="left"][trx_sc_promo title_style="default" title_align="center" link_style="default" size="normal" title="Dr. Shyam Sunder (Vaastu Consultant)" description="Dr. Sham sunder is the founder of ASTRA VEDIC VASTU and a pioneer in the area of Astrology, Numerology and Vaastu Solutions without Demolitions. He was born into a family of priests in Kollur, Karnataka in 1954 which has added to his expertise. His 40 years of experience helps in rightly understanding the concerns of the clients and provide them with customised solutions across borders."][/trx_sc_promo][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Dr. Sowmya" tab_id="1553235071396-4f6a6be8-e721"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner icons_position="left"][trx_sc_promo title_style="default" title_align="center" link_style="default" size="normal" title="Dr. Sowmya (Dietician)" description="Dr. Sowmya has a Doctorate in Nutrition and Dietetics from King's College, London. She also is the Founder CEO of NutriGENEus, a successful diet consultancy at London. The organization specializes in Autism, ADHD, Diabetes, metabolic errors, PCOD and sports nutrition. Her work experience with NHS UK has allowed her to enhance her skill. Apart from this, she also holds internationally acclaimed degrees Nutrigenomics courses. Dr. Sowmya is a specialist in DNA based diet counselling. She also had the privilege of working in London Olympics and Paralympics 2012."][/trx_sc_promo][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_tabs][vc_empty_space height="80px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="1" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" hide_bg_image_on_tablet="" hide_bg_image_on_mobile="" css=".vc_custom_1517996204203{background-color: #ffffff !important;}"][vc_column width="1/6" icons_position="left"][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/3" icons_position="left"][vc_empty_space height="120px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="1" hide_on_tablet="1" hide_on_mobile="1"][vc_empty_space height="80px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="1" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile="1"][vc_empty_space height="50px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="1" hide_on_notebook="1" hide_on_tablet="1" hide_on_mobile=""][trx_sc_title title_style="default" title_tag="h3" title_align="center" link_style="default" title="Our Values" description="#E-8_"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/6" icons_position="left"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" hide_bg_image_on_tablet="" hide_bg_image_on_mobile="" css=".vc_custom_1552635198175{background-color: #ffffff !important;}" el_class="value-icons"][vc_column width="1/3" hide_bg_image_on_tablet="" hide_bg_image_on_mobile="" column_align="center" icons_position="left" css=".vc_custom_1555051570067{padding-right: 2.1428rem !important;padding-left: 2.1428rem !important;background-color: #f3f2f0 !important;}"][vc_empty_space height="50px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="1" hide_on_tablet="1" hide_on_mobile="1"][vc_icon icon_fontawesome="icon-009_meals" color="custom" align="center" css_animation="bounceInLeft"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1563254197634{background-color: #f3f2f0 !important;}"]</p>
<h6>Get Back to Your Life</h6>
<p style="text-align: justify !important; font-size: 16px;">Our in-house rehabilitation services use the latest advances in technology to ensure our residents receive the highest level of service available.</p>
<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="50px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3" hide_bg_image_on_tablet="" hide_bg_image_on_mobile="" column_align="center" icons_position="left" css=".vc_custom_1517995294119{padding-right: 2.1428rem !important;padding-left: 2.1428rem !important;}"][vc_empty_space height="50px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="1" hide_on_tablet="1" hide_on_mobile="1"][vc_icon icon_fontawesome="icon-015_medical-care" color="custom" align="center" css_animation="bounceInRight"][vc_column_text]</p>
<h6>24/7 Availability</h6>
<p style="text-align: justify !important; font-size: 16px;">Whether it be about therapy options, nursing solutions, the admissions process, or insurance questions, we are available to answer any questions you may have regarding skilled nursing facilities.</p>
<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="50px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3" hide_bg_image_on_tablet="" hide_bg_image_on_mobile="" column_align="center" icons_position="left" css=".vc_custom_1555051555417{background-color: #f3f2f0 !important;}"][vc_empty_space height="50px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="1" hide_on_tablet="1" hide_on_mobile="1"][vc_icon icon_fontawesome="icon-014_diet" color="custom" align="center" css_animation="bounceInRight"][vc_column_text]</p>
<h6>Excellent Quality of Life</h6>
<p style="text-align: justify !important; font-size: 16px;">We have an array of social, recreational and religious activities within our bright and cheery surroundings that allow residents to enjoy their stay.</p>
<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="50px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" hide_bg_image_on_tablet="" hide_bg_image_on_mobile="" css=".vc_custom_1562150940422{background-color: #ffffff !important;}"][vc_column icons_position="left"][trx_sc_button type="default" new_window="" align="center" text_align="center" icon_position="left" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile="" link="http://www.project.razorbee.com/manasum/contact-us/" title="Contact Us" css=".vc_custom_1562150953410{margin-top: 30px !important;}"][vc_empty_space height="30px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="1" hide_on_notebook="1" hide_on_tablet="1" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_empty_space height="80px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="1" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile="1"][vc_empty_space height="120px" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="1" hide_on_tablet="1" hide_on_mobile="1"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column icons_position="left"][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>
